; Coverage test for amount.cc
; "Incorrect use of decimal comma" error
; When using decimal comma style, a comma after a period is invalid
; because the period is treated as thousands separator and only one
; decimal comma is allowed

commodity 1.000,00 EUR

2024/01/01 Bad amount
    Expenses:Food       1.000,00,50 EUR
    Assets:Checking

test bal -> 1
